lead_paragraph: The Dallas Cowboys' rookie tandem of quarterback Dak Prescott and running back Ezekiel Elliott lifted the Cowboys to a 31-17 triumph over the Chicago Bears on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Rookies Lead Cowboys to Easy Win Over Bears
